</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Tim Graham</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 01 May 2018 21:05:15 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://www.djangoproject.com/weblog/2018/may/01/bugfix-releases/</guid></item><item><title>Django bugfix releases: 2.0.4 and 1.11.12</title><link>https://www.djangoproject.com/weblog/2018/apr/02/bugfix-releases/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Today we've issued the &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/stable/releases/2.0.4/"&gt;2.0.4&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class="reference external" href="https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/stable/releases/1.11.12/"&gt;1.11.12&lt;/a&gt;  bugfix releases.&lt;/p&gt;
